 sp\u00f8r om jakken var r\u00f8d, eller hvilken farge jakken hadde, sier Magnussen.", "Retten ble i dag lukket n\u00e5r dommeravh\u00f8ret av 10-\u00e5ringen skulle spilles av. Det er derfor ikke mulig \u00e5 si noe om det ble stilt \u00e5pne eller lukkede sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5l under avh\u00f8ret."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag|overhalladrapene"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "1fb36f64b2351b9c61c8a033908c1e42106e423bbaa777bb8fdb54bfcda8b396"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-05-29T12:16:24.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Ekspert p\u00e5 vitnepsykologi, Svein Magnussen, sier barns forklaringer i retten er like troverdige som voksnes \u2013 forutsatt at sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5lene er riktig stilt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1200847.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/drapetstripe466"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/fc4ecd0279b7a731ffb76a03c3e307bd60f1b934.jpg?597e1706"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Barn er troverdige vitner -adressa.no", "Tillit viktig", "God hukommelse", "Var for ledende sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5l"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "fc4ecd0279b7a731ffb76a03c3e307bd60f1b934"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag", "overhalladrapene"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["ledende sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5l", "troverdige vitner", "barn", "sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5l", "forklarte"]}, {"field": "kw-entit